## 🏗️ II. ARQUITECTURA

### 2.1 Capas del sistema

| Capa | Archivos | Descripción |
|:-----|:--------:|:------------|
| **Pages** | 9 | Entry points por rol RBAC |
| **Views** | 69 | Componentes de vista por dominio |
| **UI Components** | 16 | Primitivos reutilizables |
| **Common Components** | 20 | Layout, Nav, Sync bridges |
| **Auth Components** | 5 | Login, Register, Demo, MFA |
| **Hooks** | 30 | Lógica reutilizable |
| **Services** | 49 | Lógica de negocio |
| **Repositories** | 30 | Abstracción de datos |
| **Stores (Zustand)** | 8 slices | Estado global |
| **Contexts** | 2 | Auth + Messaging |
| **Edge Functions** | 9 | Servidor autorizado |
| **SQL Migrations** | 2 | 3,064 LOC |

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Frontend (React 19 + Vite 7)"
        Pages["9 Pages (RBAC)"]
        Views["69 Views"]
        UI["16 UI Primitives"]
        Common["20 Common Components"]
        Hooks["30 Custom Hooks"]
        Stores["Zustand (8 slices)"]
        Contexts["2 Contexts"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Abstraction Layer"
        Services["49 Services"]
        Repos["30 Repositories"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Backend (Supabase)"
        Edge["9 Edge Functions (1,488 LOC)"]
        RLS["140 RLS Policies"]
        DB["PostgreSQL (~15 tablas)"]
        Realtime["Realtime Channels"]
        IndexedDB["IndexedDB (Dexie, 9 tablas)"]
    end

    Pages --> Views --> UI
    Views --> Hooks
    Hooks --> Services
    Services --> Repos
    Repos --> Edge
    Edge --> DB
    Repos -.-> DB
    Stores --> Views
    Contexts --> Pages
    Realtime -.-> Stores
    IndexedDB -.-> Services
```

