| Vitest | ✅ | 1,697 tests |
| CI/CD pipeline | ❌ | No hay GitHub Actions / Vercel |
| Staging env | ❌ | Solo local + Supabase Free |
| Monitoring | ❌ | Sin Sentry / DataDog |
| Logging centralizado | ❌ | Solo console.log (11 instancias) |
| Performance budgets | ❌ | Sin Lighthouse CI |
